# Drop your custom Odoo 19 addons here.
# Each addon is a folder with __manifest__.py at its root, e.g.
#
# addons/
#   my_custom_module/
#     __manifest__.py
#     __init__.py
#     models/
#     views/
#     ...
#
# The folder is bind-mounted into the container at /mnt/extra-addons,
# which is already on Odoo's addons_path.
#
# After adding or changing a module:
#   docker compose restart odoo
#
# Then go to:
#   Apps → Update Apps List
# inside Odoo.
